Here's an AgentFacts schema following the NANDA protocol for myapp.io:

```json
{
  "@context": "https://agentfacts.org/schema/v1",
  "@type": "Agent",
  "id": "https://myapp.io/.well-known/agent.json",
  "name": "MyApp Agent",
  "description": "AI-powered SaaS agent providing text and image processing capabilities via myapp.io",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "url": "https://myapp.io",
  "provider": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "MyApp",
    "url": "https://myapp.io",
    "contact": "support@myapp.io"
  },
  "capabilities": [
    {
      "@type": "Capability",
      "id": "text-processing",
      "name": "Text Processing",
      "description": "Generate, analyze, summarize, and transform text content",
      "modality": "text",
      "inputFormats": ["text/plain", "text/markdown", "application/json"],
      "outputFormats": ["text/plain", "text/markdown", "application/json"]
    },
    {
      "@type": "Capability",
      "id": "image-processing",
      "name": "Image Processing",
      "description": "Generate, analyze, and transform images",
      "modality": "image",
      "inputFormats": ["image/png", "image/jpeg", "image/webp"],
      "outputFormats": ["image/png", "image/jpeg", "image/webp"]
    }
  ],
  "authentication": [
    {
      "@type": "AuthMethod",
      "scheme": "oauth2",
      "flows": {
        "authorizationCode": {
          "authorizationUrl": "https://myapp.io/oauth/authorize",
          "tokenUrl": "https://myapp.io/oauth/token",
          "refreshUrl": "https://myapp.io/oauth/token/refresh",
          "scopes": {
            "text:read": "Read text processing results",
            "text:write": "Submit text processing requests",
            "image:read": "Read image processing results",
            "image:write": "Submit image processing requests",
            "profile": "Access basic profile information"
          }
        },
        "clientCredentials": {
          "tokenUrl": "https://myapp.io/oauth/token",
          "scopes": {
            "text:read": "Read text processing results",
            "text:write": "Submit text processing requests",
            "image:read": "Read image processing results",
            "image:write": "Submit image processing requests"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "endpoints": {
    "api": "https://api.myapp.io/v1",
    "discovery": "https://myapp.io/.well-known/agent.json",
    "documentation": "https://docs.myapp.io",
    "healthCheck": "https://api.myapp.io/v1/health"
  },
  "interoperability": {
    "protocols": ["NANDA/1.0", "MCP/1.0"],
    "a2aCompatible": true,
    "mcpEndpoint": "https://mcp.myapp.io/sse"
  },
  "trust": {
    "verificationUrl": "https://myapp.io/.well-known/agent.json",
    "signingKeyUrl": "https://myapp.io/.well-known/jwks.json",
    "termsOfService": "https://myapp.io/terms",
    "privacyPolicy": "https://myapp.io/privacy"
  },
  "rateLimit": {
    "requestsPerMinute": 60,
    "requestsPerDay": 10000,
    "burstLimit": 10
  },
  "metadata": {
    "created": "2026-03-05T00:00:00Z",
    "updated": "2026-03-05T00:00:00Z",
    "license": "proprietary",
    "tags": ["text", "image", "saas", "multimodal"]
  }
}
```

This should be served at `https://myapp.io/.well-known/agent.json` for automatic NANDA discovery.

**Key design decisions:**

- **Dual OAuth2 flows** — `authorizationCode` for user-delegated access (interactive apps), `clientCredentials` for machine-to-machine (server agents)
- **Scoped permissions** — text and image capabilities are independently scoped so agents can request minimal access
- **MCP endpoint** — included for compatibility with the Model Context Protocol agent ecosystem
- **JWKS endpoint** — enables other agents to verify signed responses from your agent
- **`a2aCompatible: true`** — signals readiness for Google's Agent-to-Agent protocol, which complements NANDA

To make discovery work, also add this to your HTML `<head>`:

```html
<link rel="agent" type="application/json" href="/.well-known/agent.json" />
```
